# pybank_slip

A framework-agnostic Python library to manage Brazilian bank slips (boletos) across multiple banks using standard HTTP libraries.
Currently supports Banco do Brasil and Santander.

## Features
- Agnostic design pattern (Strategy/Adapter).
- Standard operations: Generate, List, Edit, Cancel.
- Specific bank features like Santander Workspaces.
